data.description: Welcome to the perfect home for first-time buyers, families, or savvy investors! This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bath house is nestled in a gated community in the heart of the North West, offering both security and convenience. The 1561 square foot property boasts a great floor plan with 2 bedrooms and living space downstairs, while the primary bedroom and spacious kitchen are located upstairs. The large island in the kitchen is perfect for family gatherings and entertaining, and all appliances are included for your convenience.Community amenities are aplenty, with a refreshing pool and a charming park for residents to enjoy. The location is simply unbeatable - situated close to schools, shopping centers, and a variety of restaurants.Parking will never be an issue with a private 2 car garage making it easy to come and go as you please. Don't miss this opportunity to call this beauty your new home or investment. Schedule a tour today.
